This project automates testing of the demo e‑commerce web application SauceDemo.
The objective is to validate core functionalities such as login, product selection, cart operations, checkout, sorting, and reset state.
The framework is built using Robot Framework with a modular Page Object Model (POM) design, data‑driven testing, and professional reporting.

Test Suite Coverage:
- Login Tests: Valid/invalid users, locked‑out user, logout
- Cart Tests: Cart icon visibility, random product selection, cart validation
- Checkout Tests: Order summary, screenshot capture, confirmation message
- Sorting Tests: Validate sorting options (price, name)
- Reset Tests: Validate “Reset App State” functionality

